project.title: Fantasy Map
project.description: As part of a RPG worldbuilding project, this fantasy map of the 'Bay Idilica & Sunbridge' features illustrated icons of noteworthy locations in and around the medieval Kingdom of Aquardie. Counties and Duchies are marked with the heraldry of the noble houses who rule them.
project.seo: Custom fantasy map, city and heraldry illustration for D&D (Dungeons & Dragons)  and RPG (Roleplaying Game)
